tid":1414714,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"掟核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n只係想提醒同行要保持冷靜"},{"pid":"2ac209944cd261d05f9f86f4142b28f490600e28","tid":1414714,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"根本一班5毛帶風向。<br />\n次次一有新嘢實有一班撚屌撲出黎話咁唔得咁唔得。點知之後次次都得。<br />\n圍狗總有係。<br />\n衝立法會又係。<br />\n<br />\n係咁loop你唔悶我都悶。"},{"pid":"45d2f66645c4923a56090d7756fd273fdbff4e9e","tid":1414714,"uid":259515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f172e57139838fa1641db4ebd364c32277ce521","tid":1414714,"uid":20696,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"可能會嚇到和理非<br />\n諗辦法補救加返分<br />\n例如文宣煲大義士救老人家<br />\n要令和理非覺得自己仲係正義一方<br />\n而唔係上晒腦嘅暴力分子<br />\n<br />\n但割又好唔割又好<br />\n都應該係今晚後嘅討論<br />\n而家同路人喺出面受緊苦<br />\n我相信內心再唔贊同放火嘅人<br />\n都唔會呢刻衝出嚟譴責割蓆<br />\n所以一毛一定係多數<br />\n當然最大危機係今晚到聽朝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n勸告同割蓆要分好清楚"},{"pid":"f280501bde1f876bea415316aa1147e1da80b2e3","tid":1414714,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"唔好比仇恨衝昏頭腦"},{"pid":"80383edf0c96b515f48ca1cb96aadf3952bd3baf","tid":1414714,"uid":213935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"不篤灰，不割𥱊，槍口一致對外"},{"pid":"42ef8eba109d0f0ab86ddf3ec7abb38094f2728f","tid":1414714,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"682c32ab4709f5821c7783ddd2fb293681f7be53","tid":1414714,"uid":177213,"like":395,"dislike":17,"score":378,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"因為割嘅唔係連登仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係三毛</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"0f97785e266bf54035b7bd4c3f1c09d97d14db81","tid":1414714,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:33:24.